## 7. DESIGN SYSTEM REFERENCE

### Color (light mode, woodsy/warm)
- `--bg-canvas: #FAF7F2` (warm cream, never pure white)
- `--text-primary: #2A1F1A` (warm near-black, dark walnut)
- `--brand-primary: #C2410C` (burnt sienna — the squirrel-rust action color)
- `--accent-forest: #15803D` (deep work, "found it")
- `--accent-honey: #D97706` (energy, alerts, urgency)
- `--accent-moss: #65A30D` (light work, success)
- `--accent-acorn: #92400E` (caution, never alarm)

Dark mode shifts to "working by firelight" — deep walnut backgrounds with lifted sienna and amber accents. Full token set in `tailwind.config.ts` once implemented.

### Typography
Inter for UI, JetBrains Mono for numerals/timers. Display type only for greetings, Now Mode prompts, and empty state headlines. Standard scale from `display` (32px) down to `caption` (12px).

### Motion
- `ease-out-soft: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)` — default
- Durations: instant 120ms / quick 200ms / smooth 320ms / deliberate 480ms
- Nothing snaps. Nothing bounces aggressively. Reduced-motion fully respected.

### Component conventions
- Card radius: 20px default (calmer than typical 12-16px)
- Touch targets: 44×44px minimum
- Stash entries get organic radius (`rounded-[28px_24px_26px_22px]`) for acorn-like feel
- Pomodoro sticky card uses brand-primary (sienna) background, switches to forest on break

### Logo
Simple, friendly squirrel silhouette with slight head-tilt — curious, not frantic. Used as favicon, PWA icon, occasional empty-state accent. Never animated obnoxiously.

(Full design system maintained separately in `DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` once we move beyond FluidCalendar's existing styling patterns.)

