**Starting any session**:
> "Read WORKING_NOTES.md and tell me what's next."

**When proposing a change, Claude Code should**:
1. Identify which feature area in this document the change relates to
2. Check it against the ADHD-Native Interaction Rules
3. Surface any tradeoffs or risks
4. Show the proposed change before applying it
5. Update WORKING_NOTES.md after each session

**Ending any session**:
> "Update WORKING_NOTES.md with: what we did, what's working, what's broken, what's the very next step. Be specific enough that I can pick up cold."

**When stuck**:
> "I'm stuck on [thing]. Don't fix it for me yet. Ask me 3 clarifying questions to figure out what I actually need."

